data.title: Rev Cecil Ray “C. R.” Turner (1895
data.meta_description: Cecil Ray Turner was born March 28, 1895, in Monroe County, Kentucky, and grew up on a farm in that state, until he moved to Illinois in 1915, where he continued tilling the soil, until 1926. In that year he purchased a blacksmith shop in Kemp, Ill. He obeyed his Lord in baptism in 1913, and in 1920 began occasional...
